                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-67-off367 t18280529-67-cd368"></join>, 1 purse, value 1d.; 2 sovereigns, 9 shillings, and 1 sixpence, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18280529-67-victim470" type="victimName">
                        Oliver 
                        Beman
                     <interp inst="t18280529-67-victim470" type="surname" value="Beman"></interp>
